Jess Richards https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jess_Richards 0 Jess Richards (1943 – November 1994), born Richard Sederholm, was a Broadway actor as well as performing in many off Broadway shows. He received the Theatre World Award for best actor in a musical for his performance in On the Town in 1971.
